{"tid":1299320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我迫不及待好想遊行了。","createTime":"2019-07-09T04:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T10:09:32.000Z","uid":119729,"like":148,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"08ec7bca6785e2b78173da59d6691af847a29ff7","tid":1299320,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:38:39.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社運接軌， <br />\n示威後要拼盡全力 訴求，拿取民意。 <br />\n會首先經 上水花園第一號 進場,先拿標語。 <br />\n然後一邊遊行一邊派傳單，以最快速度趕走水貨客。 <br />\n成功KO大陸人後，我才能繼續到沙田政府合署，為DQ議員平反。 <br />\n(撤惡法，釋義士，雙普選，去調查濫權的狗) <br />\n永續 Basic Law, 將來就可以用法律監管政治各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責下次遊行和示威，勇武派聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為民主制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入立法會。 <br />\n簡直是泛民主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想遊行了。"},{"pid":"dba20acb83ff1e14fba4421f14da268e17d91f79","tid":1299320,"uid":222302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02747f6859d057a6f20e7741c2651844f0bca21","tid":1299320,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82aeb79689a68709efe87095adeb5b3bf27f8b05","tid":1299320,"uid":276274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"係政府逼大家出嚟"},{"pid":"c7a804893b2884456e2bb2f4dddd3d90138ab0db","tid":1299320,"uid":119729,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"82aeb79689a68709efe87095adeb5b3bf27f8b05","tid":1299320,"uid":276274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"係政府逼大家出嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:41:18.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n以前就話想快d星期六日放假<br />\n而家係想快d星期六日遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上左癮"},{"pid":"69cd7373892a663c478f52b679b29afba57fd5bd","tid":1299320,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:41:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-si